      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty car and I'd love for it to go to a great home! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your adventures. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and still looks wonderful parked in the driveway. If you're looking for a dependable ride that feels just right, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
