    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This powerplant features individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, screaming to an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. The chassis maintains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a weight-optimized five-link rear suspension. Recent service includes throttle actuator maintenance and a comprehensive fluid flush, ensuring the VANOS system and valvetrain operate with precision. This is a driver-oriented example with excellent mechanical feedback and a linear power band.",
