    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure? This car has been my trusty companion and it still runs like a dream! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, with just the right amount of character you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s actually been enjoyed. It\u2019s reliable, smooth, and honestly just a blast to drive. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner very happy. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
