      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900-RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec Variable M Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings, and the braking system features ventilated rotors with consistent pedal feel. While the exterior shows minor evidence of its performance history, the drivetrain remains robust and the power delivery is linear across the entire rev range. A driver-spec icon ready for the enthusiast who values mechanical integrity over a garage-queen status.",
